{"tid":1550562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"〔突發〕藍絲政黨朋友通水，藍絲宣傳策略大改","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T13:46:12.000Z","uid":77905,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8736a347ed771edaa6701f45676f7ad3e2280b0c","tid":1550562,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:35:31.000Z","msg":"自從facebook封鳩晒藍絲假新聞後<br />\n大量支持警察既假新聞post同page都收撚晒皮<br />\n有fd做某政黨<br />\n目前佢地做緊既就係要突破盲腸，主要重\b心係：<br />\n大部分對己方有利既假新聞會被ban<br />\n唯一突破方式就係利用黑衫自己網絡進行散佈<br />\n黑衫因為本身基數大，背景亦都分散<br />\n容易信既，半信半疑，到唔容易信既各有一大班人<br />\n<br />\n試諗要突破既方法好簡單，就係 炒車資訊戰<br />\n三個階段：起步，滾動，收成期<br />\n<br />\n首先提供大量資訊，越詳細越好，最好詳細到<br />\n1）多數人無時間睇 <br />\n2）容易信既一批人首先信，再將資訊既簡約版炒熱<br />\n3）連帶半信半疑一班都信<br />\n用呢個手法，最少已經造成一個三分二人buy既局面<br />\n然後利用個慣性將個topic推起佢，推到返唔到轉頭<br />\n最緊要將key information收起，於收成期利用<br />\n<br />\n直到收成期到<br />\n將key information利用各渠道發佈<br />\n炒車將大力摧毀以後所有暴徙製造新聞題材能力<br />\n重覆三次將可以將黑衫帶風向能力減至threshold以下<br />\n<br />\n以上就係呢個technique所有描述<br />\n<br />\n至於整體佈局，整個行動分三層<br />\n國際帶風向：流出聲帶、宣佈撤回<br />\n示威者風向：開學作機會宣佈撤回、炒車資訊戰<br />\n牆內風向：新聞系統重要人物來港，過去反對撤回，利用了解香港情況過程，隨後急轉彎出文配合支持撤回<br />\n<br />\n利申：以上全為9UP，自己諗"},{"pid":"00f1f9f5b56a4b290de5533a3d01a33b3ea71961","tid":1550562,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"229313d01b31c8111920b406e7191f5b74e24454","tid":1550562,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"25b06e72c1f13139ca847f3d50ae8cd3dabe8404","tid":1550562,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"35fd5e174df7c346ad8ceaa4f04bdc969cd5ec43","tid":1550562,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:38:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9085fd645a0942bf9c1c81d5b295ea8ce5b3bda","tid":1550562,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f46040f7a6dd85465625bc9cfae4a869aa10a017","tid":1550562,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47a00e8ec036a8bf76282f7cf5d21e3d5583dcf3","tid":1550562,"uid":129783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"我都唔明推多咁831 做乜⋯<br />\n是但貼張WhatsApp 圖就信哂"},{"pid":"79a80869bc5edabf97a36cf190eda88870297cc7","tid":1550562,"uid":234679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:41:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cd528ebf48a260fefdf0104291b950c35a7cd124","tid":1550562,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:42:27.000Z","msg":"做到既唔多<br />\n<br />\n睇緊呢個post既各位藍絲朋友<br />\n你呢杖係靚波既<br />\n不過就即管等星期一美國國會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808d6138c1edbe1d5bd75e660ed89a689d06eb3a","tid":1550562,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"800ade5dce6afb8e9762696711de8546ee2f0761","tid":1550562,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47a00e8ec036a8bf76282f7cf5d21e3d5583dcf3","tid":1550562,"uid":129783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"我都唔明推多咁831 做乜⋯<br />\n是但貼張WhatsApp 圖就信哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"無論死人與否 速龍都一定係超過份曼力<br />\n推831拎cctv冇問題喎<br />\n我都唔明你唔明咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec01c8eacf90139d088501e6cfeb7d11d5e0b2f6","tid":1550562,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都唔明推多咁831 做乜⋯<br />\n是但貼張WhatsApp 圖就信哂</blockquote>無論死人與否 速龍都一定係超過份暴力<br />\n推831拎cctv冇問題喎<br />\n我都唔明你唔明咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1527043274df666fca30cd0dc5d894095b954e18","tid":1550562,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:44:17.000Z","msg":"Fc"},{"pid":"aec903d1b9f915aa4834c4c9fde7b218c00b2736","tid":1550562,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"800ade5dce6afb8e9762696711de8546ee2f0761","tid":1550562,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47a00e8ec036a8bf76282f7cf5d21e3d5583dcf3","tid":1550562,"uid":129783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"我都唔明推多咁831 做乜⋯<br />\n是但貼張WhatsApp 圖就信哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"無論死人與否 速龍都一定係超過份曼力<br />\n推831拎cctv冇問題喎<br />\n我都唔明你唔明咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:46:13.000Z","msg":"推cctv係好事<br />\n<br />\n重點係個火喉要控制好<br />\n煲湯先至會靚<br />\n唔好俾佢燶"},{"pid":"05dfd627621732b1142bcf036643ce4e1a385af7","tid":1550562,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"靠香港人自己心水清唔清<br />\n長期抗爭<br />\n謠言止於智者"},{"pid":"2415f5fd12b3c5d503fdbb999f5976b6fa42522a","tid":1550562,"uid":32187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:48:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60100214f40a548a5868e563cb6f3da2b591f884","tid":1550562,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"民建聯成功爭取撒回<br />\n同埋er er sir 話褲袋藏武士刀<br />\n<br />\n哩兩個都超快瘋傳<br />\n但最起馬民建聯個個係假到爆 都瘋傳<br />\n<br />\n以家最危險嘅就係 強姦 同殺人事件<br />\n不過哩兩個對家都好難令我地炒到車<br />\n因為強姦 佢無方法拎到證據證明自己係清白<br />\n而831 cctv 佢地就算無打死人<br />\n都一定有用超暴力私刑<br />\n所以一定唔敢公開cctv"},{"pid":"3254e253ce842bbe78da722796ed40c8d1dd369a","tid":1550562,"uid":252207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"由雨傘開始 FC都係好重要 唔好輕易亂信"},{"pid":"e194e5bcf8174ded6125e565b3ef6d6b9d3a4284","tid":1550562,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"柳俊江 Lauyeah<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「未 Fact Check」、「希望炒車」⋯謠言滿天飛的日子，除非把握真憑實據，否則隨便湊合附和，實在有點不負責任。<br />\n<br />\n為甚麼謠言會傳播？社會心理學家曾經提出過：<br />\n<br />\nR (Rumor) &asymp; i (importance) &times; a (ambiguity) <br />\n[Psychology of Rumor, Allport and Postman (1947)]<br />\n<br />\n意思是謠言的力度，是其背後的重要性乘以模糊度。注意，不是「加」，是「乘」（Multiply）。重要性和模糊度任何一個元素的增長，都足以令謠言的力度倍數加強。<br />\n<br />\n先講模糊。政府各部門已經用力澄清，「沒有在執法中出現死亡個案」，本應一點不含糊。過往做傳媒的經驗，人命傷亡數字，以官方公佈為依歸，從來是可信，市民也少有異議。為甚麼2019年的今天，政府（尤其是警方）的公佈，其公信力如此低下？引用裁判法院檢控主任協會主席黃華芬的公開信一段：「Please advise the police on this important matter of honesty and reliability affecting the legal system of Hong Kong.」除了司法制度，市民的信任何嘗不是首當其衝，被毀於一旦？當記者鏡頭外的恐慌不能靠政府釐清，市民自然置身於迷霧裡。<br />\n<br />\n至於重要性，由6月開始，整個社會無意間在散播一種恐怖：「不知道第一條人命在甚麼時候犧牲。」植根於每一個人心中，其一是出人命對事態走向的影響，其二是關顧自身和親友的安全。隨著警察武力的瘋狂升級，以及更多在暗角的行徑，例如新屋嶺懷疑虐犯、警黑合作、武警混入疑雲，種種表象無不是走向市民心底恐𢣷的實現。到太子封站，秘而不宣，直接引爆各種謠言，這是必然的後果。<br />\n<br />\n事情還沒完沒了，因為對一般市民而言，「寧可信其有」，口耳相傳危機意識，不論是否有事實根據，起碼可作「善意提醒」，又或「尋求真相」之出發點，這是群眾心理走向使然。然後，更多的「證據」出現，很多的自殺和浮屍，因為心理上的自我實現傾向，相信政府隱瞞真相的人，自然認定是「政府陰謀」。雖然邏輯地說，我們不能排除其他可能性：例如是正常數字在大眾關注下產生了放大效應，又或是悲情城市引爆更多不幸自殺個案⋯不過，似乎再難以有權威去說服任何人。<br />\n<br />\n廢話了這麼多，不是說要去否定，或去認定某一面推崇的「真相」，我也難似掌握任何真憑實據。坦白說，在這個氛圍裡，我也難去信任任何一個官方證詞，情緒十分困擾。冷靜下來，想指出的是，這種不信任的發酵，十分有可能是下一個引爆社會事件升級的近因，各方不能不察。而反過來有心利用謠言，製造事件的任何人，也應該三思可能帶來的後果。<br />\n<br />\n很多人謂政府需有「大智慧」去解決問題。我肯定地說，「大誠信」來得更為迫切，更為重要。"},{"pid":"75042b93f03ea68b40ea14803b49ae1d48f47511","tid":1550562,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05dfd627621732b1142bcf036643ce4e1a385af7","tid":1550562,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"靠香港人自己心水清唔清<br />\n長期抗爭<br />\n謠言止於智者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:54:29.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\ntruly hope so"},{"pid":"288cda17102919d20ab65bb7e7f4357de4bf0d81","tid":1550562,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:54:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ffdd77495b664ac848ab3ee193a10ce187af77f3","tid":1550562,"uid":38805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec01c8eacf90139d088501e6cfeb7d11d5e0b2f6","tid":1550562,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都唔明推多咁831 做乜⋯<br />\n是但貼張WhatsApp 圖就信哂</blockquote>無論死人與否 速龍都一定係超過份暴力<br />\n推831拎cctv冇問題喎<br />\n我都唔明你唔明咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"重點住煲暴力, 無差別攻擊市民, 有人被黑警打至失去意識不知生死.<br />\n<br />\n如懷疑手足被打死, 可以講成多日未能聯絡個位手足未知生死, 太子站封站懷疑清洗証據.<br />\n<br />\n唔洗係咁講係有人死 但完全冇資料同証據."},{"pid":"55bc08bccc31bf64d8544ee85ac141a9f5e60fb9","tid":1550562,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6974d7e8aeef74a7d46303755b518b1e4f8f6cb9","tid":1550562,"uid":107405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:25.000Z","msg":"改佢老母啦<br />\n有班黑狗係到繼續打人打到血肉橫飛<br />\n藍絲點宣傳 都有佢地係到倒米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}